[{"title":"Hello World","url":"/2022/09/01/hello-world/","content":"<p>Welcome to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/\">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html\">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Quick-Start\"><a href=\"#Quick-Start\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Quick Start\"></a>Quick Start</h2><h3 id=\"Create-a-new-post\"><a href=\"#Create-a-new-post\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Create a new post\"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo new <span class=\"string\">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html\">Writing</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Run-server\"><a href=\"#Run-server\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Run server\"></a>Run server</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/server.html\">Server</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Generate-static-files\"><a href=\"#Generate-static-files\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Generate static files\"></a>Generate static files</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html\">Generating</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Deploy-to-remote-sites\"><a href=\"#Deploy-to-remote-sites\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Deploy to remote sites\"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html\">Deployment</a></p>\n","categories":["hexo博客"],"tags":["教程"]},{"title":"Hexo博客初步搭建","url":"/2022/09/01/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/hexo%E7%AB%99%E7%82%B9%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95/","content":"<p>参考文章：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/26625249/\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/26625249\\</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/60578464\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/60578464</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"搭建计划：\"><a href=\"#搭建计划：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"搭建计划：\"></a>搭建计划：</h2><ul>\n<li><input checked=\"\" disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> 设定主题为next</li>\n<li><input checked=\"\" disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> 版权声明</li>\n<li><input checked=\"\" disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> 导航栏配置</li>\n<li><input checked=\"\" disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> 侧边栏头像</li>\n<li><input disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> 侧边栏社交小图标-b站未完成</li>\n<li><input checked=\"\" disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> 显示阅读进度</li>\n<li><input checked=\"\" disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> 增加搜索功能</li>\n<li><input checked=\"\" disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> 修改文章底部标签图标</li>\n<li><input checked=\"\" disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> 文章末尾增加本文结束</li>\n<li><input checked=\"\" disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> 网站底部增加访问量</li>\n<li><input checked=\"\" disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> 增加字数统计</li>\n<li><input checked=\"\" disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> 设置网站的图标</li>\n<li><input checked=\"\" disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> 博文置顶配置</li>\n<li><input disabled=\"\" type=\"checkbox\"> </li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"解决方案\"><a href=\"#解决方案\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"解决方案\"></a>解决方案</h2><p>将hexo根目录下的.deploy_git/删除掉，然后使用hexo deploy重新部署就可以了。<br>但是暂时不清楚是什么原因引起的错误。</p>\n<p>可以hexo d但是在打开网站后只能看到readme文件。</p>\n<p>原因在于没有设置默认分支为master。自动建立了一个main branch。</p>\n<p>在设置中设置默认分支，并删除掉main branch。</p>\n<p>删除.deploy_git，并重新hexo d</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://picgo-ry.obs.cn-south-1.myhuaweicloud.com/1662046825295-7e21c2e8-9190-4735-8547-7d58502824a3.png\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<p>现在可以在<a href=\"https://rongyel.github.io/\">https://rongyel.github.io/</a></p>\n<p>看到自己的博客界面啦。</p>\n<p>更换为next主题后，本地服务可以看到页面已经换了</p>\n<p>但是.io的页面还是原来的样子。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://picgo-ry.obs.cn-south-1.myhuaweicloud.com/1662047399987-fa958900-f5f9-47cf-b8ea-4bf4f7a17989.png\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<p>npm install hexo-renderer-pug hexo-renderer-stylus –save</p>\n<p>安装以后再hexo d</p>\n<p>不知道为什么就可以了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://picgo-ry.obs.cn-south-1.myhuaweicloud.com/1662047471308-3cd2c599-ad34-4c5a-8557-b253bbbfcd35.png\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<p>每次hexo d推送之前，最好先清除浏览器的缓存。不然会发现没有变化。</p>\n<p>因为我已经搭建好图床了，所以从语雀移植过来的图片需要进行重新上传。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/351031589\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/351031589</a></p>\n<p>对自己的页面进行一些配置</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/28128674\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/28128674</a></p>\n<p>改变图标</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/qq_43340547/article/details/120581558\">https://blog.csdn.net/qq_43340547/article/details/120581558</a></p>\n<p>总是不成功……b站的图标一直没搞出来</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://picgo-ry.obs.cn-south-1.myhuaweicloud.com/bilibili.svg\" alt=\"bilibili\"></p>\n<p>算了，搞不定</p>\n<p>添加搜索功能</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/fdd8e4e36c57\">https://www.jianshu.com/p/fdd8e4e36c57</a></p>\n<p>这个教程有问题</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_45877759/article/details/107141789\">https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_45877759/article/details/107141789</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://picgo-ry.obs.cn-south-1.myhuaweicloud.com/image-20220903011954966.png\" alt=\"image-20220903011954966\"></p>\n","categories":["hexo博客"],"tags":["笔记"]},{"title":"Gvim 配置文件.vimrc","url":"/2022/09/02/Gvim%20%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6.vimrc/","content":"<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th><strong>内容</strong></th>\n<th><strong>简述</strong></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>基本配置</td>\n<td>gvim自身的一些基本配置</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>自定义快捷键</td>\n<td>ii：退出插入模式<br />ww：保存文件<br />qq：退出文件</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>插件：NERDTree</td>\n<td>文件目录管理器<br /><F5>：开关列表<br />,f：定位到当前路径</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>插件：airline</td>\n<td>状态栏美化插件</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>插件：easyalign</td>\n<td>简单的代码对齐工具<br />ga=：依据等号对齐<br />ga, ：依据逗号对齐<br />ga<space>：依据空格对齐</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>插件：neocomplcache</td>\n<td>基于缓存的自动补全插件<br />回车补全选中内容<br />空格退出补全</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>插件：gruvbox</td>\n<td>非常好看的配色方案</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>插件：nerdcommender</td>\n<td>快速注释工具<br />,cc：注释整行<br />,cA：末尾增加注释<br />,cu：取消注释<br />,c<space>：自动判断注释/取消注释</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>插件：ale</td>\n<td>语法检查插件<br />使用linter：iverilog<br />ctrl + k/j：跳到上/下一个错误点<br />* 需补充安装iverilog</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>插件：ctags</td>\n<td>tag管理插件（光标置于名称上）<br />终端命令：ctags -R 生成当前路径下所有文件的tags<br />gi：进入例化模块或输出端口<br />go：跳出到上级模块<br />* 非插件包，需补充安装</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>插件：vloginst</td>\n<td>Verilog模块自动例化插件<br />,ig：生成例化代码，后粘贴使用</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>插件：snipmate</td>\n<td>代码片段展开插件，不依赖python等环境！<br /><tab>：展开代码片段<br />ctrl+<tab>：展开可能匹配的代码片段列表</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>新建文件自动添加文件头</td>\n<td>新建*.v,<em>.sv,</em>.cpp,<em>.c,</em>.h类型文件自动生成</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>保存更新文件头修改时间</td>\n<td>在保存文件时，自动更新文件头中的修改时间文本</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<figure class=\"highlight verilog\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;</span> basic configuration </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">syntax on &quot;</span> syntax highlight</span><br><span class=\"line\">filetype plugin indent on  <span class=\"string\">&quot; plugins and indentation based on file type  </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">set hlsearch &quot;</span> search highlight</span><br><span class=\"line\">set ignorecase <span class=\"string\">&quot; ignore search case</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">set cuc &quot;</span> current column highlight</span><br><span class=\"line\">set cul <span class=\"string\">&quot; current line highlight</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">set nu &quot;</span> show line number</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">set fileencoding=utf-<span class=\"number\">8</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;prevent garbled characters</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">set fenc=utf-8</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">set fencs=utf-8,usc-bom,euc-jp,gb18030,gbk,gb2312,cp936,big－5                    </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">set enc=utf-8</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">source $VIMRUNTIME/delmenu.vim</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">source $VIMRUNTIME/menu.vim</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">let &amp;termencoding=&amp;encoding</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">set guifont=Monospace\\ 13 &quot;</span> set font </span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">set tabstop=<span class=\"number\">4</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot; set tab to 4 spaces</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">set expandtab</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">set shiftwidth=4 &quot;</span>set auto-indent to <span class=\"number\">4</span> spaces</span><br><span class=\"line\">set softtabstop=<span class=\"number\">4</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot; set the back key to delete 4 spaces</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">set ruler &quot;</span> set show ruler</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">set smartindent <span class=\"string\">&quot; set smart auto-indent</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">set showcmd &quot;</span> show command</span><br><span class=\"line\">set autochdir  <span class=\"string\">&quot; auto-swith working directory</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">winpos 235 235 &quot;</span> set windows position </span><br><span class=\"line\">set lines=<span class=\"number\">40</span> columns=<span class=\"number\">108</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot; set windows size </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">set nocompatible &quot;</span> remove vi consistency</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;</span> customize shortcut keys </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">imap ii &lt;ESC&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">map ww :w&lt;CR&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">map qq :q&lt;CR&gt; </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">let mapleader = &quot;</span>,<span class=\"string\">&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;</span>-----------------------------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot; plugin: NERDTree</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;</span>-----------------------------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class=\"line\">map &lt;leader&gt;ne :NERDTreeToggle&lt;CR&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">let</span> g:NERDTreeWinSize = <span class=\"number\">25</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot; set nerdtree size</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">let NERDTreeIgnore=[&#x27;\\.pyc&#x27;,&#x27;\\~$&#x27;,&#x27;\\.swp&#x27;] &quot;</span> ignore the display of the following files</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">let</span> NERDTreeShowHidden=<span class=\"number\">1</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot; show hidden files</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">let g:NERDTreeDirArrowExpandable = &#x27;▸&#x27; &quot;</span> modify the <span class=\"keyword\">default</span> arrow symbol</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">let</span> g:NERDTreeDirArrowCollapsible = &#x27;▾&#x27;</span><br><span class=\"line\">autocmd bufenter * <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (winnr(<span class=\"string\">&quot;$&quot;</span>) == <span class=\"number\">1</span> &amp;&amp; exists(<span class=\"string\">&quot;b:NERDTree&quot;</span>) &amp;&amp; b:NERDTree<span class=\"variable\">.isTabTree</span>()) | q | endif</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot; nerdtree hot key mapping</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">map &lt;F5&gt; :NERDTreeMirror&lt;CR&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">map &lt;F5&gt; :NERDTreeToggle&lt;CR&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">map &lt;leader&gt;f :NERDTreeFind&lt;CR&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;</span>-----------------------------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot; plugin: airline</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;</span>-----------------------------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">let</span> g:airline_theme=<span class=\"number\">&#x27;ba</span>se16_gruvbox_dark_hard&#x27;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;</span> plugin: indentline</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">let g:indentLine_enable = 1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">let g:autopep8_disable_show_diff=1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">let g:indentLine_char_list = [&#x27;|&#x27;, &#x27;¦&#x27;, &#x27;┆&#x27;, &#x27;┊&#x27;]</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;</span>-----------------------------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot; plugin: easyalign</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;</span>-----------------------------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot; Start interactive EasyAlign in visual mode (e.g. vipga)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">xmap ga &lt;Plug&gt;(EasyAlign)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;</span> Start interactive EasyAlign <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> a motion/text object (e<span class=\"variable\">.g</span>. gaip)</span><br><span class=\"line\">nmap ga &lt;Plug&gt;(EasyAlign)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;</span> plugin: neocomplcache</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">let g:neocomplcache_enable_at_startup = 1 &quot;</span> auto start neocomplcache  </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">let</span> g:neocomplcache_enable_auto_select = <span class=\"number\">1</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot; auto select the first item in the list</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">let g:neocomplcache_min_syntax_length = 2 &quot;</span> Set minimum syntax keyword length.</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">let</span> g:neocomplcache_lock_buffer_name_pattern = &#x27;\\*ku\\*&#x27;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot; inoremap &lt;expr&gt;&lt;CR&gt;  neocomplcache#smart_close_popup() . &quot;</span>\\&lt;CR&gt;<span class=\"string\">&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">inoremap &lt;expr&gt;&lt;C-Y&gt;  neocomplcache#close_popup()</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">inoremap &lt;expr&gt;&lt;space&gt;  neocomplcache#undo_completion()</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">inoremap &lt;expr&gt;&lt;Enter&gt;  pumvisible() ? &quot;</span>\\&lt;C-Y&gt;<span class=\"string\">&quot; : &quot;</span>\\&lt;Enter&gt;<span class=\"string\">&quot;  </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;</span>-----------------------------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot; plugin: gruvbox</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;</span>-----------------------------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class=\"line\">set bg=dark</span><br><span class=\"line\">colorscheme gruvbox</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;</span> plugin: nerdcommender</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;</span> my key: ,cl /,cc /,cu /,c&lt;space&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">let</span> g:NERDSpaceDelims = <span class=\"number\">1</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot; add space after comment</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;</span>-----------------------------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot; plugin: ale</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;</span>-----------------------------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;keep the sign gutter open</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">let g:ale_sign_column_always = 1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">let g:ale_sign_error = &#x27;&gt;&gt;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">let g:ale_sign_warning = &#x27;--&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;</span> show errors <span class=\"keyword\">or</span> warnings in my statusline</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">let</span> g:airline#extensions#ale#enabled = <span class=\"number\">1</span> </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot; use quickfix list instead of the loclist</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">let g:ale_set_loclist = 0</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">let g:ale_set_quickfix = 1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;</span> only enable these linters</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">let</span> g:ale_linters = &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\\    &#x27;verilog&#x27;: [&#x27;iverilog&#x27;]</span><br><span class=\"line\">\\&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">nmap &lt;silent&gt; &lt;C-k&gt; &lt;Plug&gt;(ale_previous_wrap)</span><br><span class=\"line\">nmap &lt;silent&gt; &lt;C-J&gt; &lt;Plug&gt;(ale_next_wrap)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;</span> plugin: ctags</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;-----------------------------------------------------------------------------</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">nmap gi &lt;C-]&gt; &quot;</span> go into <span class=\"keyword\">instance</span> <span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <span class=\"keyword\">or</span> <span class=\"keyword\">output</span> port </span><br><span class=\"line\">nmap go &lt;C-o&gt; <span class=\"string\">&quot; go out to upper stage </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;</span>-----------------------------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot; pl